hen they leave our website and to read the privacy statements of each and every website that collects personally identifiable information. The aforementioned Privacy Policy Agreement applies only and solely to the information collected by our website.\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: bold;">Security </span>\r\n\r\nFlat Vernacular LLC shall endeavor and shall take every precaution to maintain adequate physical, procedural and technical security with respect to our offices and information storage facilities so as to prevent any loss, misuse, unauthorized access, disclosure or modification of the user\'s personal information under our control.\r\n\r\nThe company also uses Secure Socket Layer (SSL) for authentication and private communications in an effort to build users\' trust and confidence in the internet and website use by providing simple and secure access and communication of credit card and personal information.\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: bold;">Changes to Privacy Policy Agreement </span>\r\n\r\nFlat Vernacular LLC reserves the right to update and/or change the terms of our privacy policy, and as such we will post those change to our website homepage at www.deptofdecoration.com, so that our users and/or visitors are always aware of the type of information we collect, how it will be used, and under what circumstances, if any, we may disclose such information. If at any point in time Flat Vernacular LLC decides to make use of any personally identifiable information on file, in a manner vastly different</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="page" title="Page 3">\r\n<div class="section">\r\n<div class="layoutArea">\r\n<div class="column">\r\n\r\nfrom that which was stated when this information was initially collected, the user or users shall be promptly notified by email. Users at that time shall have the option as to whether or not to permit the use of their information in this separate manner.\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: bold;">Acceptance of Terms </span>\r\n\r\nThrough the use of this website, you are hereby accepting the terms and conditions stipulated within the aforementioned Privacy Policy Agreement. If you are not in agreement with our terms and conditions, then you should refrain from further use of our sites. In addition, your continued use of our website following the posting of any updates or changes to our terms and conditions shall mean that you are in agreement and acceptance of such changes.\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: bold;">How to Contact Us </span>\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions or concerns regarding the Privacy Policy Agreement related to our website, please feel free to contact us at the following email, telephone number or mailing address.\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: bold;">Email: </span>info@deptofdecoration.com\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: bold;">Telephone Number: </span>3474576227\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: bold;">Mailing Address: </span>\r\n\r\nFlat Vernacular LLC\r\n35 Meadow St Suite 214 Brooklyn, New York 11206\r\n\r\n05/14/2014\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '194-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-13 14:00:35', '2014-05-13 14:00:35', '', 194, 'http://www.deptofdecoration.com/wordpress/194-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (402, 1, '2014-05-13 14:42:20', '2014-05-13 14:42:20', '<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-226" src="http://www.deptofdecoration.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/diamond.png" alt="diamond" width="35" height="34" /> [box]<strong> Dining Room: Revelation</strong>. <span style="color: #222222;">To put it simply, we believe in decoration. We want to #decorateeveryday and #decoratetheeveryday. </span> Each Department of Decoration collection will launch with an event, whether a dinner, a performance, or an intimate party in an unexpected place. That\'s because we think it\'s important that you get to interact with our products before making a purchase--and because we selfishly want to see you live inside our little D o D world, if only for a few hours.\r\n\r\n[/box]', 'Gatherings', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '122-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-13 14:42:20', '2014-05-13 14:42:20', '', 122, 'http://www.deptofdecoration.com/wordpress/122-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (401, 1, '2014-05-13 14:36:11', '2014-05-13 14:36:11', '<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-226" src="http://www.deptofdecoration.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/diamond.png" alt="diamond" width="35" height="34" />\r\n\r\n[box]<strong> Dining Room: Revelation</strong>.\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #222222;">To put it simply, we believe in decoration. We want to #decorateeveryday and #decoratetheeveryday. </span>\r\n\r\nEach Department of Decoration collection will launch with an event, whether a dinner, a performance, or an intimate party in an unexpected place. That\'s because we think it\'s important that you get to interact with our products before making a purchase--and because we selfishly want to see you live inside our little D o D world, if only for a few hours.\r\n<div style="color: #222222;">Our first collection focuses on our personal favorite room of any home - the dining room. In celebration, D o D and the <a href="http://www.ssssociety.com/">Spring Street Social Society</a>, will host series of four dinner parties from <span class="aBn" tabindex="0" data-term="goog_688785023"><span class="aQJ">May 14-17</span></span> in downtown Manhattan featuring our new ceramics, textiles, and flatware.</div>\r\n<div style="color: #222222;"></div>\r\n<div style="color: #222222;">Our next collection, produced in part with luxury lingerie company <a href="http://www.fleurdumal.com/">Fleur du Mal</a>, will be for the bedroom. Check back soon for more information.</div>\r\n<div style="color: #222222;"></div>\r\n<div style="color: #222222;">Check back soon for more information.</div>\r\n[/box]', 'Gatherings', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '122-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-13 14:36:11', '2014-05-13 14:36:11', '', 122, 'http://www.deptofdecoration.com/wordpress/122-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
