ine themes in that it features a super minimalist design with an emphasis o\'>WPTavern: Semicolon is Possibly the Cleanest Free Magazine Theme for WordPress</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wordpress.tv/2014/06/05/brad-parbs-writing-extensible-plugins/\' title=\'\'>WordPress.tv: Brad Parbs: Writing Extensible Plugins</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=\'dashboard-news-plugin\'><span>Popular Plugin:</span> <a href=\'http://wordpress.org/plugins/wordfence/\' class=\'dashboard-news-plugin-link\'>Wordfence Security</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=\'plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=wordfence&amp;_wpnonce=841bf45ea8&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800\' class=\'thickbox\' title=\'Wordfence Security\'>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'); 
